<div class="jumbotron" id="tablesJumbotron">
    <div class="container" id="jumbotroncontainer">
        <h1 id="HeaderText" class="text-center">Mission Statement</h1>

    </div>
</div>

<p>
    <br />

    The Goal of my personal Red Badge MVC is to create a search system and store for people looking to add/create a specific feel within their own home.
    This store will separate itself by focusing on allowing the user to search for decor by using specific adjectives such as modern, vintage, even wabi sabi.
    Plus if an item pertains to multiple adjective categories you’ll be able to find that Item in all of the categories that apply.
    Ever end up scrolling through lists upon lists of furniture items that you would never use? Feel like you waste time trying to
    find the perfect art print to match a specific room? Look no further, this is the app for you.
</p>
